因此执行请求应该是DecodeJob的Run方法。
DecodeJob的Run方法@Override
public void run() {
  GlideTrace.beginSectionFormat("DecodeJob#run(model=%s)", model);
  DataFetcher localFetcher = currentFetcher;
  try {
  //如果取消了加载就回调失败
    if (isCancelled) {
      notifyFailed();
      return;
    }
    //执行加载
    runWrapped();
  } catch (CallbackException e) {
    throw e;
  } catch (Throwable t) {
   //捕获打印日志
    if (Log.isLoggable(TAG, Log.DEBUG)) {
      Log.d(
          TAG,
          "DecodeJob threw unexpectedly" + ", isCancelled: " + isCancelled + ", stage: " + stage,
          t);
    }
    // 失败执行
    if (stage != Stage.ENCODE) {
      throwables.add(t);
      notifyFailed();
    }
    if (!isCancelled) {
      throw t;
    }
    throw t;
  } finally {
    // Keeping track of the fetcher here and calling cleanup is excessively paranoid, we call
    // close in all cases anyway.
    if (localFetcher != null) {
      localFetcher.cleanup();
    }
    GlideTrace.endSection();
  }
}

DecodeJob的runWrapped方法:private void runWrapped() {
  switch (runReason) {
    case INITIALIZE:
      //初始化加载
      stage = getNextStage(Stage.INITIALIZE);
      currentGenerator = getNextGenerator();
      runGenerators();
      break;
    case SWITCH_TO_SOURCE_SERVICE:
      //从磁盘或网络加载
      runGenerators();
      break;
    case DECODE_DATA:
      //解析资源
      decodeFromRetrievedData();
      break;
    default:
      throw new IllegalStateException("Unrecognized run reason: " + runReason);
  }
}
在DecodeJob初始化时，默认runReason为INITIALIZE。因此走到INITIALIZE分支：
在这里调用了      stage = getNextStage(Stage.INITIALIZE);
      currentGenerator = getNextGenerator();
      runGenerators();
依次查看下这三个方法。
DecodeJob的getNextStage()、getNextGenerator()、runGenerators()方法：
getNextStage()方法：private Stage getNextStage(Stage current) {
  switch (current) {
    case INITIALIZE：
      //如果可以从磁盘中加载到解码的缓存资源的话就返回标记，否则就循环查看是否其余资源缓存
      return diskCacheStrategy.decodeCachedResource()
          ? Stage.RESOURCE_CACHE
          : getNextStage(Stage.RESOURCE_CACHE);
    case RESOURCE_CACHE:
      //查看是否有下载的未解码的源数据缓存
      return diskCacheStrategy.decodeCachedData()
          ? Stage.DATA_CACHE
          : getNextStage(Stage.DATA_CACHE);
    case DATA_CACHE:
      //从数据源获取    
      //没有缓存就需要加载数据、如果设置了只从缓存中获取就直接返回结束
      // Skip loading from source if the user opted to only retrieve the resource from cache.
      return onlyRetrieveFromCache ? Stage.FINISHED : Stage.SOURCE;
    case SOURCE:
    case FINISHED:
      return Stage.FINISHED;
    default:
      throw new IllegalArgumentException("Unrecognized stage: " + current);
  }
}
经过该方法 stage这个变量应该储存要发起哪种获取（磁盘缓存还是源数据获取）。

getNextStage()方法：
private DataFetcherGenerator getNextGenerator() {
    switch (stage) {
      case RESOURCE_CACHE:
        return new ResourceCacheGenerator(decodeHelper, this);
      case DATA_CACHE:
        return new DataCacheGenerator(decodeHelper, this);
      case SOURCE:
        return new SourceGenerator(decodeHelper, this);
      case FINISHED:
        return null;
      default:
        throw new IllegalStateException("Unrecognized stage: " + stage);
    }
  }
根据之前getNextStage函数判断的应该从哪里加载返回不同的DataFetcherGenerator实现类。
runGenerators()方法：
 private void runGenerators() {
    currentThread = Thread.currentThread();
    startFetchTime = LogTime.getLogTime();
    boolean isStarted = false;
    //正常情况下由currentGenerator.startNext()执行判断是否成功
    while (!isCancelled
        && currentGenerator != null
        && !(isStarted = currentGenerator.startNext())) {
      stage = getNextStage(stage);
      currentGenerator = getNextGenerator();
      //如果是从源数据加载，重新启动加载
      if (stage == Stage.SOURCE) {
        reschedule();
        return;
      }
    if ((stage == Stage.FINISHED || isCancelled) && !isStarted) {
    //如果重试也失败会走到这里
        notifyFailed();
    }

    // Otherwise a generator started a new load and we expect to be called back in
    // onDataFetcherReady.
  }
在实际中会调用currentGenerator.startNext()来判断加载是否成功
由于getNextStage函数会返回三种不同的DataFetcherGenerator实现类：ResourceCacheGenerator、DataCacheGenerator、SourceGenerator。可以逐步查看三种类的startNext方法。

ResourceCacheGenerator、DataCacheGenerator、SourceGenerator的startNext方法：
ResourceCacheGenerator的startNext方法：
public boolean startNext() {
  //获取缓存key
  List sourceIds = helper.getCacheKeys();
  if (sourceIds.isEmpty()) {
    return false;
  }
  //获取在初始化时注册的可被转换解析的所有类型
  List> resourceClasses = helper.getRegisteredResourceClasses();
  if (resourceClasses.isEmpty()) {
    if (File.class.equals(helper.getTranscodeClass())) {
      return false;
    }
    throw new IllegalStateException(
        "Failed to find any load path from "
            + helper.getModelClass()
            + " to "
            + helper.getTranscodeClass());
  }
  //尝试20次 在循环在可解析类型集合中查找要解析的类直到第一次成功
  while (modelLoaders == null || !hasNextModelLoader()) {
    resourceClassIndex++;
    if (resourceClassIndex >= resourceClasses.size()) {
      sourceIdIndex++;
      if (sourceIdIndex >= sourceIds.size()) {
        return false;
      }
      resourceClassIndex = 0;
    }
    //获得对应的缓存
    Key sourceId = sourceIds.get(sourceIdIndex);
    Class resourceClass = resourceClasses.get(resourceClassIndex);
    //取得解码后的转换
    Transformation transformation = helper.getTransformation(resourceClass);

    currentKey =
        new ResourceCacheKey( // NOPMD AvoidInstantiatingObjectsInLoops
            helper.getArrayPool(),
            sourceId,
            helper.getSignature(),
            helper.getWidth(),
            helper.getHeight(),
            transformation,
            resourceClass,
            helper.getOptions());

     //获取到对应的磁盘缓存资源文件
    cacheFile = helper.getDiskCache().get(currentKey);
    if (cacheFile != null) {
      sourceKey = sourceId;
      //获得注册的解码加载器
      modelLoaders = helper.getModelLoaders(cacheFile);
      modelLoaderIndex = 0;
    }
  }

  loadData = null;
  boolean started = false;
  while (!started && hasNextModelLoader()) {
     //遍历解码器
    ModelLoader modelLoader = modelLoaders.get(modelLoaderIndex++);
    //创建一个解码数据类型
    loadData =
        modelLoader.buildLoadData(
            cacheFile, helper.getWidth(), helper.getHeight(), helper.getOptions());
    // helper.hasLoadPath(loadData.fetcher.getDataClass()这句代码说明解码器可以解码该类型
    if (loadData != null && helper.hasLoadPath(loadData.fetcher.getDataClass())) {
      //只有解码成功才会走到这里
      started = true;
      //调用解码器解析数据
      loadData.fetcher.loadData(helper.getPriority(), this);
    }
  }
  return started;
}
可以看到最终调用的是loadData.fetcher.loadData(helper.getPriority(), this);这个方法解码数据，因此要找到该fetcher对应的具体初始化地方，可以看到loadData数据是由modelLoader.buildLoadData方法生成，modelLoader是由对应的类获取到的解码器，回到modelLoader的初始化地方，看下Glide默认注册了那些解码器：
